    <thetext>Benjamin,

what do you mean?

Actual we have the following metadata:

metaData={task.meta.readOnly=false, task.meta.type=person, task.meta.label=QA Contact:}

So you can use TaskAttribute.TYPE_PERSON.equals(attribute.getMetaData().getType()) for this.</thetext>
