    <bug_when>2013-03-08 04:29:38 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>The problem I was facing was this: I was iterating trough all the different attributes to show the user only those he should be touching. My filtering was based on the idea that all attributes with a kind can be managed by the user (vs. internal helper attributes). Only for person attributes, bugzilla uses no kind at all where I&apos;d expect to see @TaskAttribute#KIND_PEOPLE@ instead of null. But maybe I&apos;m on the wrong track there.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
