    <bug_when>2013-03-08 14:46:03 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>OK now I know what you need.

Actual we only have TaskAttribute.KIND_DEFAULT for none hidden Attribute and null for hidden attributes.

TaskAttribute.KIND_DEFAULT is used to manage which Attributes are shown in the Attributes Section.

Please look into https://git.eclipse.org/r/11000.</thetext>
